comment_text:
After 3rd dose of pfizer, I experienced shortness of breath at the end of 2nd weeks. The symptoms persists after a month since the first episode.

At first, Want to call post vaccine hotline? No hotline.

Went to gp, gp said may not be related to vaccine.

Went to pulmonologist, doctor said it's getting common after people are vaccinated (booster). Air ways are more sensitive.i was given meds and asthma medicine, symptoms not clear but slightly better.

Not sure if anyone else encounter similar post vaccine (booster) issues but it seems to me too much vaccines can be risky.

Note: what eventually helps is plenty of rest and TCM. Changing diet to Low carb and no caffeine. Symptoms not clear but improving.
